[08:16] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'visual references, visual anchors. If you don\'t anchor your prompt with something tangible, you\'re going to get what the AI wants to give you by default. And by default, I don\'t think you\'re going to be happy. Like yes,'

