[09:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'match confidence. Basically, if the images aren\'t that close together in look, it\'s going to be hard for the anchor to push them together. I think that sort of makes sense. So, at least I warned you about that here. The anchor'

[09:59] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
